answers:

])

question: What are the survival chances of allgery House dust mite (organism)?
answers:
db.patients.aggregate([
  { $match: {"ENCOUNTERS.ALLERGIES.DESCRIPTION": "House dust mite (organism)"} },
  { $unwind: "$ENCOUNTERS" },
  { $unwind: "$ENCOUNTERS.ALLERGIES" },
  { $match: {"ENCOUNTERS.ALLERGIES.DESCRIPTION": "House dust mite (organism)"} },
  { $group: {_id: "$ENCOUNTERS.ALLERGIES.DESCRIPTION", survival_chances: { $avg: "$ENCOUNTERS.ALLERGIES.SURVIVAL_CHANCES" } } },
  { $project: { _id: 0, survival_chances: 1 } }
])
